dct_description_sm: Compiled chiefly from the Surveys by Captains Flinders, Blackwood, Stanley, Yule & Denham, R.N. 1802-60; with additions from various Surveys to 1885 ; The North east Coast of New Guinea by Captain Moresby and Lieutt. Dawson, R.N. 1874, with corrections from the German Government Chart of 1913 ; Engraved by Edwd. Weller ; Published...under the Superintendence of Captain W.J.L. Wharton, R.N. Hydrographer.
Depths shown by soundings; relief by hachures and spot heights
Emergency Reproduction of B.A. Chart - June 1942; April 1943
Shows coasts, shoals, reefs, islands, ports, drainage, vegetation.
